@Generated(value="com.guidewire.pl.metadata.codegen.Codegen", comments="ArchivedClaimSearchEntity.eti;ArchivedClaimSearchEntity.eix;ArchivedClaimSearchEntity.etx") public class ArchivedClaimSearchEntity extends SolrSearchEntity
ArchivedClaimSearchEntity Supports the efficient creation of archived claim lists returned through ClaimCenter's archived claim solr search function. This is a virtual entity and is not stored in the database.
